      <h2>2. No Media Hosting</h2>
      <p>We do not store or download any media files on our physical databases. Our search engine extracts download URLs directly from third-party hosting servers (e.g., YouTube CDN, Facebook, Instagram) that serve public video content. Users are responsible for obtaining permissions from copyright owners before using any downloaded media.</p>

