      <p>By using our website or app, you hereby consent to our disclaimer and agree to its terms. We comply with all DMCA copyright procedures. If you are a copyright owner or an agent thereof and believe that any content fetched via Vidra infringes upon your copyrights, you may request that our server filters out specific URLs by sending a notice to our contact support.</p>
